OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 29 MAR
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1960FThe 5th Eurovision Song Contest
OL,7,Fairs on BBC TV. It's held at the Royal
OL,8,FFestival Hall in London. Katie Boyle
OL,9,Fpresented the show. France wins the
OL,10,Fcontest with the song Tom Pillibi,
OL,11,Fperformed by Jacqueline Boyer. Bryan
OL,12,FJohnson came 2nd for the UK.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1971FThe first edition of Sesame
OL,15,FStreet airs on ITV (HTV). LWT and
OL,16,FGrampian would be the next ITV regions
OL,17,Fto air the programme, on 25th September
OL,18,F1971.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG1977FThe first episode of Warship
OL,21,Fairs on BBC One.
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
